# Shell directory contract

**Replaces:** `workbench-directory.mdc`, `app-shell-directory.mdc`
**Doctrine:** ADR-0001 (Spatial OS), ADR-0005 (shell unification). If this rule and `AGENTS.md` diverge, follow `AGENTS.md`.

---

## Route layout facade (`AppShell` / `AppSubLayout`)

- **`app/**/layout.tsx`** should import **`AppShell`** and **`AppSubLayout`** from **`#components/workbench`** — they are **re-exports** of `WorkbenchShell` / `WorkbenchSubLayout` in [`app-shell.ts`](../../components/workbench/app-shell.ts) with **no wrapper component** (same function reference).
- **Filesystem and implementation** stay under `workbench-*.tsx`; **`WorkbenchShell` / `WorkbenchSubLayout` remain exported** from the workbench barrel for compatibility and tests.

---

## Boundary split

| Directory | Owns | Does NOT own |
|---|---|---|
| **`components/workbench/`** | All post-login layout chrome: `WorkbenchShell`, `WorkbenchSubLayout`, `WorkbenchSurface`, utility bar, `WorkbenchRail`, command layer, dock, mobile rail, skip-to-main | Product surfaces, ERP logic, DB access, Server Actions |
| **`components/nexus/`** | Nexus Field product surface (`nexus-page.tsx` + zone components) and Lynx summon UI (`nexus-lynx-summon*.tsx`) | Shell chrome (belongs in `components/workbench/`) |
| **`components/auth/`** | IAM surfaces (sign-in, interruption flows) | — |

> `components/nexus/` is no longer the shell host. **`AppShell`** (alias of `WorkbenchShell`) is the single canonical post-login mount from `app/**/layout.tsx`.

